      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>The Christian collection of the apocryphal Acts of the Apostles is the main
            Ethiopian collection of apostolic Apocrypha. It includes single texts, mainly
            Preaching, Martyrdom, and Acts of the Apostles, translated from Arabic. The terminus ante quem for the collection is provided by  <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet52">BNFet52</t:ref>, datable to <t:date>1379</t:date>. However,
            the title G.Ḥ. already appears in an inventory of books found in the
            well-known <t:date notBefore="1200" notAfter="1300">thirteenth-century</t:date> Four Gospels manuscript (<t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1832">EMML 1832</t:ref>) of
            Ḥayq ʾƎsṭifānos (the so-called Four Gospels book of ʾIyasus Moʾa). Six recensions are known according to <t:bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PMRJZ4A4"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Bausi2000Osservazioni"/><title level="a">Alcune osservazioni sul Gadla ḥawāryāt</title><title level="j">Annali dell’Istituto Orientale di Napoli</title><author><forename>Alessandro</forename><surname>Bausi</surname></author><date>2000</date><biblScope unit="volume">60-61</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">77-114</biblScope><note type="url">https://www.academia.edu/1151410/Alcune_osservazioni_sul_Gadla_%E1%B8%A5aw%C4%81ry%C4%81t</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Bausi2000Osservazioni</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Bausi2000Osservazioni</note></t:bibl>, depending on the Vorlage and the selection and order of texts, see <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5811GHI">Contendings of the
                                                  Apostles: Recension I</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5814GHII">Contendings of the
                                                  Apostles: Recension II</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5815GHIII">Contendings of the
                                                  Apostles: Recension III</t:ref>,
               <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5816GHIV">Contendings of the
                                                  Apostles: Recension IV</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5817GHV">Contendings of the
                                                  Apostles: Recension V</t:ref> and <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5818GHVI">Contendings of the
                                                  Apostles: Recension VI</t:ref>.</t:p>
         </t:abstract>
